3c91d30e-7b6e-4500-8b46-444ac62ab2c3.do_description: To make the output, you have to...replace the inner most color with the outer most color and complete the same step with every color until all have been changed. In other words, invert the order of the colors.
3c91d30e-7b6e-4500-8b46-444ac62ab2c3.grid_description: The output grid size...same size as the input grid.
3c91d30e-7b6e-4500-8b46-444ac62ab2c3.see_description: In the input, you should see...a grid with different colored square borders that get smaller and smaller until it reaches the center.
